OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774638672
OL,3,CWildlife park will review wolves being
OL,4,Ckept in captivity after pack euthanised
OL,6,FThe director of a wildlife park in
OL,7,FKent, which put down its entire wolf
OL,8,Fpack to stop them from killing each
OL,9,Fother, has questioned whether the
OL,10,Fanimals should be kept in captivity as
OL,11,Fhe spoke of the "heartbreaking"
OL,12,Fdecision.
OL,14,FWildwood Trust, near Canterbury,
OL,15,Feuthanised five wolves: Odin, Nuna,
OL,16,FMinimus, Tiberius and Maximus, after
OL,17,Ftheir aggression levels "exploded",
OL,18,Fleading to fights which left three of
OL,19,Fthem with life-threatening injuries.
OL,26,@sD@QOUsD@_O]yD@YOUyD@bO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/12
