OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774638672
OL,3,CWildlife park will review wolves being
OL,4,Ckept in captivity after pack euthanised
OL,6,FThe park has kept wolves in captivity
OL,7,Ffor several years to help educate its
OL,8,Fvisitors, but director general Paul
OL,9,FWhitfield said this will now be
OL,10,Freviewed.
OL,12,FMr Whitfield said: "A few weeks ago,
OL,13,Fthe level of aggression within the
OL,14,Fpack really exploded, completely
OL,15,Funexpectedly.
OL,17,F"It went from a harmonious pack, to
OL,18,Fanimals that were just fighting each
OL,19,Fother and causing each other quite
OL,20,Fserious harm.
OL,26,@tD@TOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774638672
OL,3,CWildlife park will review wolves being
OL,4,Ckept in captivity after pack euthanised
OL,6,F"It was really distressing for
OL,7,Feveryone to see it, and for the
OL,8,Fanimals.
OL,10,F"If nothing was done to intervene,
OL,11,F(the wolves would) eventually kill
OL,12,Feach other, which was a really
OL,13,Fhorrible and worrying situation," he
OL,14,Fadded.
OL,16,FAfter three wolves suffered life-
OL,17,Fthreatening injuries the park sought
OL,18,Fadvice from outside experts, before
OL,19,Fdeciding euthanasia was "the only
OL,20,Fthing" it could do.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@aO]{D@YOU|D@FO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774638672
OL,3,CWildlife park will review wolves being
OL,4,Ckept in captivity after pack euthanised
OL,6,FMr Whitfield said: "Because the pack
OL,7,Fhad broken down to the point it had,
OL,8,Fif we were to euthanise those (three)
OL,9,Fanimals and then leave the other
OL,10,F(two), those (two) would just continue
OL,11,Fto fight in the same way.
OL,13,F"It was just an awful situation to be
OL,14,Fin. At that point, the decision was
OL,15,Ftaken that the only humane thing to do
OL,16,Fwould be to euthanise all five of them
OL,17,Fat the same time.
OL,19,F"It was heartbreaking, to be honest.
OL,20,FIt was absolutely the last thing that
OL,21,Fanyone wanted to do," he added.
OL,26,@nD@TOUuD@AOU{D@AOU}D@UO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774638672
OL,3,CWildlife park will review wolves being
OL,4,Ckept in captivity after pack euthanised
OL,6,FThe incident has promoted some concern
OL,7,Famong animal welfare organisations
OL,8,Fwhich campaign against keeping animals
OL,9,Fin captivity.
OL,11,FIn response, Mr Whitfield said: "The
OL,12,Ftruth is, they're not an easy animal
OL,13,Fto keep in captivity. They are a
OL,14,Fcomplex social group and if people are
OL,15,Fgoing to keep them, they really need
OL,16,Fto understand that and talk to experts
OL,17,Fabout that.
OL,26,@sD@aOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774638672
OL,3,CWildlife park will review wolves being
OL,4,Ckept in captivity after pack euthanised
OL,6,F"I wouldn't say they should never be
OL,7,Fkept in captivity, but I think a lot
OL,8,Fof thought needs to go into whether
OL,9,Fthey should be in any case."
OL,11,FAs to whether the benefits of keeping
OL,12,Fwolves in captivity outweigh the
OL,13,Frisks, Mr Whitfield said: "That's
OL,14,Fexactly what we're going to review.
OL,15,FThat's been our position in the past.
OL,17,F"Until this event, we've been very
OL,18,Fgood at managing wolves successfully
OL,19,Fand they've been a really important
OL,20,Fpart of the way we've been able to
OL,21,Feducate people.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@\O]uD@[OUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774638672
OL,3,CWildlife park will review wolves being
OL,4,Ckept in captivity after pack euthanised
OL,6,F"But given that this has happened, I
OL,7,Fthink that we need to review that... I
OL,8,Fthink it's only right that we review
OL,9,Fthat after something like this has
OL,10,Fhappened."
OL,12,FHe added: "We didn't want at all to
OL,13,Fcover this up or hide what has
OL,14,Fhappened.
OL,16,F"It's an awful situation and we wanted
OL,17,Fto be very frank about what had
OL,18,Fhappened... we've got nothing to hide,
OL,19,Fwe can understand that people are
OL,20,Fupset, we're all deeply upset here.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@JO]tD@KOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774638672
OL,3,CWildlife park will review wolves being
OL,4,Ckept in captivity after pack euthanised
OL,6,F"There's no upside for us in this."
OL,8,FA Wildwood Trust spokesperson added:
OL,9,F"A Post Mortem from the International
OL,10,Fzoo veterinary group has confirmed
OL,11,Fthat all five wolves demonstrated
OL,12,Fwounds, injuries and pathologies that
OL,13,Fit would not have been moral, or
OL,14,Flegal, to continue with.
OL,16,F"It was agreed that prompt pack
OL,17,Feuthanasia was the only viable option
OL,18,Fat this point."
OL,26,@nD@AOUnD@cO]qD@AOUxD@AOUzD@OO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774638672
OL,3,CWildlife park will review wolves being
OL,4,Ckept in captivity after pack euthanised
OL,6,FRichard Morley, director of the Wolves
OL,7,Fand Humans Foundation, said that while
OL,8,Fthe incident raises such questions,
OL,9,Fcaptive wolves "contribute
OL,10,Fsignificantly" to education, and
OL,11,Fsupport conservation of the species in
OL,12,Fthe wild.
OL,14,FHe said: "If we hope to have wolves
OL,15,Fback in the UK one day, it is
OL,16,Fimportant that people can see them in
OL,17,Fthe flesh and learn more about them,
OL,18,Fparticularly at places like Wildwood,
OL,19,Fwhich has an excellent record in
OL,20,Fsupporting conservation and
OL,21,Freintroduction of native species."
OL,26,@qD@POUrD@NO]vD@JOU}D@bO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774638672
OL,3,CWildlife park will review wolves being
OL,4,Ckept in captivity after pack euthanised
OL,6,FBut Chris Lewis, captivity research
OL,7,Fand policy manager at Born Free, said
OL,8,Fit is "almost impossible" to maintain
OL,9,Fthe "complex and hierarchical" social
OL,10,Fgroups of species such as wolves in
OL,11,Fcaptivity, which have "nowhere to
OL,12,Fescape" from conflict.
OL,14,FMr Lewis said: "It is yet more
OL,15,Fevidence as to why species with
OL,16,Fcomplex social structures should never
OL,17,Fbe kept in captivity for the sake of
OL,18,Fpublic entertainment."
OL,26,@pD@GOUpD@YO]qD@EOUqD@^O]sD@WOUtD@GO]vD@
OL,26,APOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774638672
OL,3,CWildlife park will review wolves being
OL,4,Ckept in captivity after pack euthanised
OL,6,FElisa Allen, vice-president of the
OL,7,FPeta Foundation, said: "These wolves
OL,8,Fdid not belong in captivity, where
OL,9,Ftheir ability to spread out and form
OL,10,Fagreeable social groups is restricted
OL,11,Fto the point of causing them harm and,
OL,12,Fin this case, costing their very lives.
OL,14,F"If the Wildwood Trust cares not to
OL,15,Frepeat this tragedy, these will be the
OL,16,Flast wolves bred into a life of
OL,17,Fconfinement.
OL,26,@oD@XOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/12
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,415,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1774638672
OL,3,CWildlife park will review wolves being
OL,4,Ckept in captivity after pack euthanised
OL,6,F"Society has surely evolved enough to
OL,7,Frecognise that animals are emotional
OL,8,Findividuals with complex group
OL,9,Fbehaviours, not things to gawk at on a
OL,10,FSaturday.
OL,12,F"The only ethical focus is on
OL,13,Fprotecting habitats so that wild
OL,14,Fanimals can live where they belong."
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
OL,26,@tD@AOUvD@dO]
